'''南非農場襲擊'''（{{lang-af|Plaasaanvalle}}）是一種暴力犯罪，其行為包括謀殺、襲擊以及搶劫；這些情況在[[南非|南非]]的農場內發生<ref name="theSouthAfrican25Apr19">{{cite web|url=https://www.thesouthafrican.com/south-africa-farm-attacks-not-racially-motivated/|title=Recent spate of farm attacks dispels ‘racially motivated’ rhetoric|date=25 April 2019|website=The South African|accessdate=27 April 2019|archive-date=2019-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426142539/https://www.thesouthafrican.com/south-africa-farm-attacks-not-racially-motivated/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="702burgerafriforumworkers">{{cite web |url=http://www.702.co.za/articles/278024/more-black-farm-workers-are-killed-than-white-farm-workers |title=More black farm workers are killed than white farm workers |first=Johan |last=Burger |date=26 October 2017 |website=[[Radio_702|Radio 702]] |accessdate=20 August 2018 |archive-date=2018-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129033752/http://702.co.za/articles/278024/more-black-farm-workers-are-killed-than-white-farm-workers |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="farFromBlackWhiteSmh">{{cite news |url=https://www.smh.com.au/politics/federal/blood-in-the-dust-the-plight-of-south-african-farmers-is-far-from-black-or-white-20180622-p4zn6u.html |title=Blood in the dust: The plight of South African farmers is far from black or white |first=Jewel |last=Topsfield |date=23 June 2018 |newspaper=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] |accessdate=20 August 2018 |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406204039/https://www.smh.com.au/politics/federal/blood-in-the-dust-the-plight-of-south-african-farmers-is-far-from-black-or-white-20180622-p4zn6u.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，針對的通常是白人農民和黑人農場工人<ref name="702burgerafriforumworkers"/><ref name="farFromBlackWhiteSmh"/><ref name="Committee">{{cite web|title=Report of the Committee of Inquiry into Farm Attacks – 31 July 2003|url=http://www.saps.gov.za/statistics/reports/farmattacks/farmattacks_2003.htm|accessdate=7 December 2013|archive-date=2009-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090319232709/http://www.saps.gov.za/statistics/reports/farmattacks/farmattacks_2003.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該術語沒有正式的法律定義，但這種攻擊一直是南非以及國外媒體與公眾人物討論的主題。沒有足夠的可靠數據來估計南非農民的謀殺率<ref name="bbc2017">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-41807642|title=Are protesters right on South Africa farm murders?|date=3 November 2017|website=BBC News|accessdate=11 November 2017|archive-date=2019-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601150743/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-41807642|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據南非政府的數據顯示，在2015年至2017年期間，農場每年發生58宗至74宗謀殺案；這數字與{{le|德蘭士瓦農業聯盟|Transvaal Agricultural Union}}收集的數據基本一致<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://africacheck.org/factsheets/factsheet-statistics-farm-attacks-murders-sa/|title=FACTSHEET: Statistics on farm attacks and murders in South Africa|work=Africa Check|access-date=15 September 2018|language=en-GB|archive-date=2019-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617212134/https://africacheck.org/factsheets/factsheet-statistics-farm-attacks-murders-sa/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="news24DeadlyProvince">{{cite web|url=https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/farm-attacks-and-murders-this-is-sas-most-deadly-province-for-farmers-20180505|title=Farm attacks and murders: This is SA's most deadly province for farmers|last=Spies|first=Derrick|date=5 May 2018|website=[[News24|News24]]|accessdate=20 August 2018|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616061852/https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/farm-attacks-and-murders-this-is-sas-most-deadly-province-for-farmers-20180505|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。由於計算南非農民數量與農場謀殺案的問題，因此目前並不清楚農民是否比其他南非人更容易被謀殺<ref name="bbc2017" />。

根據[[南非|南非]]報章的報導，大多數農場攻擊者都是年輕[[黑人|黑人]]，而大多數受害者是南非的[[白人|白人]]農場主<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/africa/article7078730.ece|title=White farmers 'being wiped out'|work=Sunday Times|date=28 March 2010|author=Dan McDougall|accessdate=24 May 2011|archive-date=2010-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603141223/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/africa/article7078730.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author=Adriana Stuijt | url=http://www.digitaljournal.com/article/267463 | title=Two more S.African farmers killed: death toll now at 3,037 | publisher=Digital Journal | date=17 February 2009 | accessdate=24 May 2011 | archive-date=2011-05-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520125757/http://www.digitaljournal.com/article/267463/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但這說法經常受到異議<ref>{{cite web|last=Nechama|first=Brodie|title=Are SA whites really being killed "like flies"?|url=http://www.africacheck.org/reports/are-white-afrikaners-really-being-killed-like-flies/|publisher=Africa Check|accessdate=7 December 2013|archive-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701123659/http://africacheck.org/reports/are-white-afrikaners-really-being-killed-like-flies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雖然政府認為沒有證據顯示攻擊農場是有組織的，但白人農場主相信攻擊為了驅趕他們離開自己的農地<ref name="nyet">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1998/07/16/world/rural-white-south-africa-afraid-and-armed.html|title=Rural White South Africa: Afraid, and Armed|author=Suzanne Daley|work=New York Times|date=16 July 1998|accessdate=24 May 2011|archive-date=2014-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729115548/http://www.nytimes.com/1998/07/16/world/rural-white-south-africa-afraid-and-armed.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，極右翼政治人物[[尤金·特雷布蘭奇|尤金·特雷布蘭奇]]在他的農場被殺，引起國際社會關注南非農場受到攻擊的問題<ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/apr/04/eugene-terreblanche-south-african-white-supremacist Eugene Terre'Blanche, opponent of White farm murders is hacked to death] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/apr/04/eugene-terreblanche-south-african-white-supremacist |date=20130130101219 }} ''The Guardian''. 4 April 2010</ref>。

2015年7月，南非團體「非洲論壇」宣稱該年上半年在南非有116宗襲擊農場主事件，造成27名農場主喪生。[[新华网|新华网]]的報導宣稱南非農場主「被杀害的概率远远高于其他南非人」。從1994年至2015年，有超過3,000名白人農場主被殺害。「非洲論壇」當時宣稱有許多案件沒有被偵破，有時即使疑犯被捕也未必得到審判<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-07/06/c_1115826796.htm |title=记者手记：在刀尖上舔血——南非农场主安全状况堪忧 |publisher=新華網 |date=2015-07-06 |accessdate=2018-08-24 |archive-date=2018-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824183214/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-07/06/c_1115826796.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

